{
  "$comment": "RFC 8414 OAuth 2.0 Authorization Server Metadata. PointCast delegates OAuth to Google — authorization_endpoint is our relay, token_endpoint is Google's. Companion: /.well-known/openid-configuration, /.well-known/oauth-protected-resource.",
